  "body": "Moniker can return 5 names in a row, which are longer than the 14 character release name limit.\nThis results in tiller install unit tests periodically failing..\n### Example Failure\n\n(Below snippet from CI build @ https://circleci.com/gh/kubernetes/helm/1455)\n`2016-08-26 . | info: Candidate name \"tufted-grasshopper\" exceeds maximum length 14. Skipping.`\n`2016-08-26 . | info: Candidate name \"coiling-panther\" exceeds maximum length 14. Skipping.`\n`2016-08-26 . | info: Candidate name \"lanky-marsupial\" exceeds maximum length 14. Skipping.`\n`2016-08-26 . | info: Candidate name \"donating-possum\" exceeds maximum length 14. Skipping.`\n`2016-08-26 . | info: Candidate name \"auxilliary-moth\" exceeds maximum length 14. Skipping.`\n`2016-08-26 . | warning: No available release names found after 5 tries`\n`2016-08-26 . | Failed install prepare step: no available release name found`\n`--- FAIL: TestInstallReleaseNoHooks (0.00s)`\n`release_server_test.go:279: Failed install: no available release name found`\n### Potential Solutions\n- Add support in moniker to specify the max length of the name\n- Truncate the release name to 14 chars, whenever moniker returns one greater than 14 \n",
